---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
---

<Layout title="Legal | The Civic Chronic">
    <Header />

    <main class="flex-grow pt-32 pb-24 px-6 min-h-screen bg-gray-50">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
            <header class="mb-16 text-center border-b-4 border-ink pb-8">
                <h1
                    class="font-serif text-5xl md:text-7xl font-black text-ink mb-4 uppercase tracking-tighter"
                >
                    Terms of Submission
                </h1>
                <p
                    class="font-mono text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-widest text-sm"
                >
                    Reference No. LGL-2026-VOID // Do Not Read
                </p>
            </header>

            <article class="prose prose-lg max-w-none font-serif text-ink">
                <div
                    class="bg-white border border-gray-200 p-8 md:p-12 shadow-sm"
                >
                    <p
                        class="font-bold uppercase text-xs tracking-widest text-gray-400 mb-8 border-b border-gray-100 pb-2"
                    >
                        Last Updated: Yesterday (Maybe)
                    </p>

                    <h3
                        class="flex items-center gap-3 text-2xl font-bold uppercase tracking-tight mt-0"
                    >
                        <span
                            class="bg-ink text-white w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center text-sm rounded-sm"
                            >1</span
                        >
                        Definitions & Interpretations
                    </h3>
                    <p>
                        <strong>1.1 "The Archive"</strong> refers to <em
                            >The Civic Chronic</em
                        >, its subsidiaries, shadow organizations, and the dusty
                        server it runs on.<br />
                        <strong>1.2 "The Subject"</strong> (hereinafter "You") refers
                        to any sentient entity foolish enough to visit this website.<br
                        />
                        <strong>1.3 "Failure"</strong> refers to the state of existence.
                    </p>

                    <hr class="border-gray-200 my-8" />

                    <h3
                        class="flex items-center gap-3 text-2xl font-bold uppercase tracking-tight"
                    >
                        <span
                            class="bg-ink text-white w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center text-sm rounded-sm"
                            >2</span
                        >
                        Disclaimer of Competence
                    </h3>
                    <p>
                        The Archive makes no warranty, express or implied,
                        regarding the accuracy, reliability, or existence of the
                        content provided. We explicitly disclaim any guarantee
                        that:
                    </p>
                    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1 marker:text-gray-400">
                        <li>The website will load.</li>
                        <li>
                            The links will lead anywhere other than a 404 void.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            The typography will be legible on screens narrower
                            than a 1998 Palm Pilot.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            Any of the "facts" presented are factually factual.
                        </li>
                    </ul>

                    <hr class="border-gray-200 my-8" />

                    <h3
                        class="flex items-center gap-3 text-2xl font-bold uppercase tracking-tight"
                    >
                        <span
                            class="bg-ink text-white w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center text-sm rounded-sm"
                            >3</span
                        >
                        Limitation of Liability
                    </h3>
                    <p>
                        In no event shall The Civic Chronic be liable for any
                        direct, indirect, incidental, special, exemplary, or
                        consequential damages (including, but not limited to,
                        procurement of substitute goods or services; loss of
                        use, data, or sanity) arising in any way out of the use
                        of this website, even if advised of the possibility of
                        such damage.
                    </p>
                    <div
                        class="bg-gray-100 p-4 border-l-4 border-gray-300 italic text-sm text-gray-600 my-4"
                    >
                        "If reading our font choices causes you a migraine, that
                        is a pre-existing medical condition between you and your
                        optometrist."
                    </div>

                    <hr class="border-gray-200 my-8" />

                    <h3
                        class="flex items-center gap-3 text-2xl font-bold uppercase tracking-tight"
                    >
                        <span
                            class="bg-ink text-white w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center text-sm rounded-sm"
                            >4</span
                        >
                        Privacy & Surveillance
                    </h3>
                    <p>
                        <strong>4.1 Cookies:</strong> We use cookies solely for emotional
                        support. They do not track anything because we haven't figured
                        out how to set up Google Analytics properly.<br />
                        <strong>4.2 Data Collection:</strong> Any data you submit
                        to us (via forms, emails, or telepathy) is immediately redacted
                        and filed in a circular bin (the trash). We value your privacy
                        so much we ignore you completely.
                    </p>

                    <hr class="border-gray-200 my-8" />

                    <h3
                        class="flex items-center gap-3 text-2xl font-bold uppercase tracking-tight"
                    >
                        <span
                            class="bg-ink text-white w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center text-sm rounded-sm"
                            >5</span
                        >
                        Governing Law
                    </h3>
                    <p>
                        These Terms shall be governed by and construed in
                        accordance with the Laws of Murphy ("Anything that can
                        go wrong, will go wrong"). Any disputes arising under
                        these terms shall be subject to binding arbitration by a
                        panel of three (3) uninterested cats.
                    </p>

                    <div
                        class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t-2 border-ink flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-6"
                    >
                        <div class="text-sm font-mono text-gray-500 uppercase">
                            Status: <span
                                class="bg-red-100 text-red-600 px-2 py-1 rounded"
                                >Unsigned</span
                            >
                        </div>
                        <button
                            class="bg-gray-200 text-gray-400 px-6 py-3 font-bold uppercase tracking-wider cursor-not-allowed text-sm"
                            disabled
                        >
                            I Agree (Server Offline)
                        </button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </article>
        </div>
    </main>

    <Footer />
</Layout>
